线程基础
线程状态

graph LR
    A["创建线程对象"] -->|"new Thread()"| NEW["New"]
    NEW -->|"Thread.start()"| RUN["Runnable"]
    RUN -->|"获取锁失败"| BLOCK["Blocked"]
    BLOCK -->|"锁释放"| RUN
    RUN -->|"Object.wait(time)"| TWAIT["Timed Waiting"]
    TWAIT -->|"超时或被 notify"| RUN
    RUN -->|"Object.wait()"| WAIT["Waiting"]
